============================== 2.17.90 ============================

2006-11-10  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@gnome.org>

	* NEWS: Update some.
	* doc/reference/tmpl/gnome-print-job.sgml: gtk-doc changed this
	* doc/reference/tmpl/gnome-rfont.sgml: and this.
	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print-job.c: (gnome_print_job_print):
	Fix bug #361876 - "Crash when printing out a pdf in a directory
	with a localized name with chinese locale". Patch from Takao
	Fujiwara.
	* po/nb.po: Updated

2006-11-05  Jon K Hellan  <hellan@acm.org>

	* libgnomeprint/modules/win32/gnome-print-win32.c
	(load_paper_sources): Fix bin_cnt test.

2006-11-03  Jon K Hellan  <hellan@acm.org>

	* libgnomeprint/modules/win32/gnome-print-win32.c (paper_name,
	load_paper_sizes, load_paper_sources, append_printer,
	cb_update_status): Convert locale <-> UTF-8 where necessary. Fixes
	#369413.

2006-11-02  Jon K Hellan  <hellan@acm.org>

	* libgnomeprint/modules/win32/gnome-print-win32.c (get_model):
	Convert printer name from to UTF-8. Partial fix of #369413.

2006-10-31  Jon K Hellan  <hellan@acm.org>

	* libgnomeprint/modules/win32/gnome-print-win32.c (load_paper_sizes,
	load_paper_sources): Check for errors of DeviceCapabilities. Fixes (?)
	#309715 and #361610.

