	* Release 2.12.1

2005-09-23  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* libgnomeprint/grammar.y (gnome_print_filter_parse_prop) : Don't leak
	  refs to filters.  gnome_print_filter_append_predecessor ADDS a ref,
	  it does not absorb one.

