	(gnome_print_job_get_pages): Return number of pages after filters.
	(gnome_print_job_render_page): Render page after filters.

2005-08-15  Lutz Mueller <lutz@users.sourceforge.net>

	* libgnomeprint/Makefile.am: gnome-print-[multipage,frgba].[c,h] are no
	longer used. We use filters instead.
	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print-job.c
	(gnome_print_job_setup_context): update layout data here.
	(gnome_print_job_print)
	(gnome_print_job_render)
	(gnome_print_job_render_page): Use filters.
	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print.c: No need for special case for ps2 driver any
	more.

