	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print-ps2.c (gp_ps2_stroke): Initialize variable before using it
	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print-config.c: Bug 156415
	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print-job.c: ditto
	* libgnomeprint/gnome-print-multipage.c: ditto
	* libgnomeprint/gpa/gpa-node.c: ditto
	* tests/tools/pdfcheck.c: ditto

