	* gp-gc.h: More comments

	* gpa-private.h: Error #ifndef WE_ARE_LIBGNOMEPRINT_UI

	* gnome-print.h: More comments

	* gnome-print-private.h: Error #ifndef WE_ARE_LIBGNOMEPRINT_UI

